name: MoodTracker
0:
”Alexa, ask mood tracker to set my mood to 50”
”Alexa, ask mood tracker what is my mood”
skdetail:
Rated: Guidance Suggested. This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: mood tracker
Developer Terms of Use
des: Mood Tracker allows Alexa to track your mood by asking her to log your mood as a numerical value between 0 and 100. You can say things like "Alexa, ask mood tracker to set my mood to 50".
